snippet.title: Clevver Music
snippet.description:
Clevver Music is THE #1 source for music news, interviews and more! 

Welcome to Clevver Music! Clevver Music is your one stop shop for all things music, KPop, new artists & much more! Come join in on the fun and get entertained!  
 
We want to make Clevver Music a safe place for our hosts and our audience. Your comments are always welcome, even if they are critiques. However, we will delete your remarks if they are deemed off-topic, contain vulgar language, or are disrespectful of others.

For all business and sponsorship please reach out to maddie.conklin@hearst.com 

SUBSCRIBE!

Website: http://www.clevver.com
